author: HBO Max
description:
In Season 1, Episode 5 of Peacemaker: The Official Podcast, James Gunn, Jennifer Holland (Emilia Harcourt), and Steve Agee (John Economos), with Chukwudi Iwuji (Clemson Murn) and Lars Winther (Co-Executive Producer) takes you behind the scenes of HBO Max’s breakout series. Season 1, Episode 5, “Monkey Dorey”, explores the turning points and character arcs that mark the midpoint of the season. From John Cena’s evolution as Peacemaker to major story reveals and the growing tension within the team, this episode is packed with insider insights and creative commentary. Get exclusive on-set stories, a deeper look at the show’s action, humor, and emotional layers, and learn how Episode 5 sets the course for the explosive second half of the first season of Peacemaker. Subscribe for more easter eggs and behind-the-scenes breakdowns. New episodes drop Mondays and Thursdays. Stream Peacemaker on HBO Max
